{"tid":2170052,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【八仙飯店】黃秋生：考慮留台教戲賣「叉燒包」","createTime":"2020-08-23T03:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T00:08:48.000Z","uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94b249d9c9a31d5316f4397c5d248fbb5f8ff0e6","tid":2170052,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"明報全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20200823/s00016/1598120081711/嘆香港千瘡百孔感心噏-黃秋生考慮留台教戲賣叉燒包\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20200823%2Fs00016%2F1598120081711%2F%E5%98%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%83%E7%98%A1%E7%99%BE%E5%AD%94%E6%84%9F%E5%BF%83%E5%99%8F-%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%95%99%E5%8F%B0%E6%95%99%E6%88%B2%E8%B3%A3%E5%8F%89%E7%87%92%E5%8C%85&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=9633d87f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2Farticle%2F20200823%2Fs00016%2F1598120081711%2F%E5%98%86%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%83%E7%98%A1%E7%99%BE%E5%AD%94%E6%84%9F%E5%BF%83%E5%99%8F-%E9%BB%83%E7%A7%8B%E7%94%9F%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%95%99%E5%8F%B0%E6%95%99%E6%88%B2%E8%B3%A3%E5%8F%89%E7%87%92%E5%8C%85&h=4d09d73e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20200823/s00016/1598120081711/嘆香港千瘡百孔感心噏-黃秋生考慮留台教戲賣叉燒包</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】黃秋生在台灣完成首部台劇《四樓的天堂》返港，日前在社交平台上載外賣晚餐照，有不少網民留言問他為何不留在台灣，又叫他「快啲走」、「做乜返嚟，此地不宜久留」等。其實今年5月，秋生前往台灣拍台劇時，台灣文化部已表示歡迎黃秋生在台灣居留。秋生昨日接受《明報》電話訪問，他表示在台灣工作逗留了數個月，感覺良好，不抗拒移居當地，但不需要刻意，認為若當地有工作，留留吓就自然會留下來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生回港後正忙於搬屋，處理大量物品，單是書籍也有過萬本，他表示稍後又再赴台灣拍飲食節目，考慮在當地開班教授戲劇和<span class=\"gold\">開叉燒包店</span>，在港月租數萬元自住的房子，丟空無人住實在太浪費。他呻窮說︰「現在慳得就慳，要縮減開支，總之邊度有工作、有錢掙就去邊度，香港現在零工作，在港做乜？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DBVzF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DBVzF5.jpg&h=d3cee6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"937d860da2f46f1e384776b8299be89ab2d1f178","tid":2170052,"uid":5737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vnPf0S7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvnPf0S7.png&h=e6a53143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2aba3d84a113dda206e28723c2c304943aae1f8","tid":2170052,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"在港月租數萬元自住的房子，丟空無人住實在太浪費。<br />\n<br />\n我可以幫吓手去住吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b36947fa31e458da885543232426fb5ca9fe43","tid":2170052,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"梁粉冇job 接就洗底扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dc4fe5d9f5b99c0bc95fd9c06fa4fbfa7313e0","tid":2170052,"uid":1837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"開豆腐店仲好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8bf2600b9c7e97056bcfb71e7525e2f991291a","tid":2170052,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff4ad08aeed5c25acc2824e93dfca73ae30112c","tid":2170052,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92dc4fe5d9f5b99c0bc95fd9c06fa4fbfa7313e0","tid":2170052,"uid":1837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"開豆腐店仲好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T00:08:48.000Z","msg":"陽明山豆腐店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}